Minister of Sport, Arts and Culture Nathi Mthethwa JOHANNESBURG - Minister of Sport, Arts and Culture Nathi Mthethwa announced on Friday that the SABC will broadcast PSL matches on TV and Radio. The announcement comes after the government intervened in the battle between the PSL and SABC. Mthethwa and Communications Minister Stella Ndabeni-Abrahams announced a resolution has been found. The public broadcaster has been holding talks with the PSL for the past two weeks to end the blackout.